{"tid":433552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［很想要吧］河北男娶烏克蘭妻後攪「中烏聯姻」發大達","createTime":"2017-10-12T12:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T12:57:40.000Z","uid":41351,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d36a8523f1925df5e73b1ec5d9ed0fb4d287a8","tid":433552,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國河北省一名男子考試落榜，毅然決然到烏克蘭留學，從此人生不一樣，從魯蛇翻身一躍成為人生勝利組，還開了跨國婚介所成為富豪，羨煞不少人。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國媒體報導，原本是業餘攝影師的梅愛偲當年因為大學考試落榜，便決定到烏克蘭留學，因為到當地留學比較不注重高中成績。沒想到在烏克蘭生活後，發現這裡美女如雲，也讓他認識了現在的嬌妻妲莎。<br />\n<br />\n兩人感情漸穩並步入禮堂，跌破許多人眼鏡，紛紛來問他怎麼在異地娶到美嬌娘，讓梅愛偲發現這也許能成為商機，於是成立了跨國相親俱樂部，標榜只要30萬元人民幣（約新台幣137萬元），便能在烏克蘭娶到貌美嬌妻。<br />\n<br />\n梅愛偲指出，由於烏克蘭當地薪資不高，月薪2000多人民幣（約新台幣1萬元）就已經是不錯的待遇了，加上中國男女比嚴重失衡，常有許多「剩男」討不到老婆。因為這樣，梅愛偲跨國婚姻生意十分成功，還買下買下近千坪土地蓋豪宅，當起了大富豪。<br />\n<br />\n梅愛偲的故事爆紅後在網路上瘋傳，而本人也常在微博曬夫妻恩愛照以及妻子辣照，不少人直呼好羨慕。儘管有人質疑梅愛偲彷彿在從事婚姻的買賣，甚至是跨國賣淫，但梅愛偲否認，表示自己就如一般的相親業者，只是幫助別人搭起幸福的橋梁而已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/204026_fef9a2de2c44b34dbff44ebdb50ae8d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F204026_fef9a2de2c44b34dbff44ebdb50ae8d7.jpg&h=51226c64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/204026_2f0113506760303e4eaa9218e98bec4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F204026_2f0113506760303e4eaa9218e98bec4f.jpg&h=a4016276&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/204027_2f0113506760303e4eaa9218e98bec4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F204027_2f0113506760303e4eaa9218e98bec4f.jpg&h=4c16f2d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/204027_e3c9589965c99ef7c64c6dedcdaef41d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F204027_e3c9589965c99ef7c64c6dedcdaef41d.jpg&h=13c02af4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2c6978e17f91a61ed3337e9eb84a35e7885aa68","tid":433552,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0450bee358b9242d89e1e4a68f385741d18e212","tid":433552,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:44:16.000Z","msg":"港人月薪窮極萬二蚊，係烏克蘭可橫行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54811ed26fc6db8bc44d3b765b9ef86f8189f09","tid":433552,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"祖國啲男人真係高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a52404d886222ec1ce0b2ad287dede4adbabf61","tid":433552,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:45:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛災難警報<br />\n勿回奶西妖post</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"d9ecd0c5705089a379ea394892e81b52ab33902f","tid":433552,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/204508_bcb11f45d7454851d836cd9cbd160e06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F204508_bcb11f45d7454851d836cd9cbd160e06.jpg&h=9712de36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/204509_7a4455c358c581f17738931de35ab250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F204509_7a4455c358c581f17738931de35ab250.jpg&h=a972a4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點報名"},{"pid":"38ffc64f43241e5d6608ae87e89fe4e746cf98fd","tid":433552,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"人一世，物一世，<br />\n住公屋都屌到高質鬼妹邊度搵到<img src=\"/assets/fac